      • addZoomProperty

        public static void addZoomProperty(java.lang.String containerId)
        Adds the jquery zoom functionality on the image container element whose id is passed as a parameter.

        Parent element can be span, div or table element.

        Parameters:
        containerId - String Id of the parent element of image element. Cannot be NULL or empty.

      • removeZoomProperty

        public static void removeZoomProperty(java.lang.String containerId)
        Removes the jquery zoom functionality on the image container element whose id is passed as a parameter.

        Parent element can be span, div or table element.

        Parameters:
        containerId - String Id of the parent element of image element. Cannot be NULL or empty.

      • resizeElements

        public static void resizeElements(java.lang.String resizableId,
                  java.lang.String childId,
                  int width,
                  int height)
        Adds jquery resizable functionality to the child id passed along with the id passed as resizable.

        Width and height needs to be passed below which the element will not resize further.

        Parameters:
        resizableId - String id of element which needs to be resizable along with child id.
        childId - String id of element which needs to be resizable.
        width - minimum width of child element.
        height - maximum width of child element.
